{
  "stem": "18486.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she stayed with us forever, almost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's still my daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because when she lived in that cooped up where they brought all the Jewish people, she lived with 21 members of her family, and not one survived.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when the war was over, then we kept her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we wanted to adopt her, but the Jewish people didn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, she has to grow up in a Jewish surrounding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there wasn't a Jewish-- how do you call that-- orphanage, very near us, and that's where she was placed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the war she was with us, the whole war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't understand you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our own children?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our own children?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the older ones, they knew where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew it exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we said, go, then they knew it's coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once, one of the Jewish children stayed, had not gone away, and she was with our children, and the Germans didn't pay any attention to her.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although she was dark, and my two children were highly blonde.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As blonde as you can be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Several times.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they had a feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They always-- they came to our house because they knew there is something going on there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't know-- but we also had an artist, a Jewish artist, who falsified papers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could beautifully do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Beautiful work he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that office we had there too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kurt was his name, Kurt Delmonte.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kurt, K-U-R-T, Delmonte.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was an artist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have several of his works yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they came and knew something is going on in this house, because they came time and time again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I never broke down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kept saying, nonsense.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
